

# Choice of technology to implement application

## Context and Problem Statement

Choosing the correct technology stack in order to achieve the best result for the application


## Considered Options

* Blazor
* Javascript

## Decision Outcome

Chosen option: Blazor, the experience with blazor and the ever growing support will allow the app to be created very well. 


## Pros and Cons of the Options

### Blazor


* Good, because very strong when paired with C# knowledge
* Good, because good documentation
* Good, because can combine web languages with C# very easily
* Bad, because large file sizes


### Javascript

* Good, because widely used
* Good, because the go-to web technology
* Bad, because lack of familiarity

